@startuml CreateOrderWorkflow
title Create Order Workflow - WEB App

actor "Customer\nApp" as Customer
participant "API\nGateway" as Gateway
participant "Order\nService" as OrderService
database "Order DB" as Database

Customer -> Gateway: POST /orders\n{source: "WEB"}
activate Gateway
Gateway -> OrderService: Forward request
activate OrderService

OrderService -> Database: CREATE Order\nstatus=CREATED
activate Database
Database --> OrderService: Order{id, createdAt, status}
deactivate Database

OrderService --> Gateway: HTTP 201 Created
deactivate OrderService
Gateway --> Customer: Order{id, source, status, items=[]}
deactivate Gateway

note over OrderService
  Order initialized with:
  - Unique UUID generated
  - Source recorded (WEB)
  - Status: CREATED
  - Empty items array
  - totalPrice: 0
end note
@enduml
